## 🎨 Design System

### Colors

- **Backgrounds** → `bg-black` (main), `bg-gray-900` (sections)
- **Text** → `text-gray-300` (primary), `text-gray-400` (secondary), `text-gray-500` (muted)
- **Accents (max 2 per section)**

  - Cyan → Standard / info
  - Fuchsia → Premium / highlights
  - Rose → Warnings / costly
  - Green → Benefits / savings
  - Purple → Dates / implementation

### Gradients

- Hero → radial cyan+fuchsia glow
- CTA → cyan → black radial fade

