## 📐 Layout & Structure

### Global Layout

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
  <body class="bg-black">
    <!-- Fixed nav (home/back) -->
    <div class="scroll-container">
      <!-- Full-screen scroll-snap sections -->
    </div>
    <!-- Footer (optional) -->
  </body>
</html>
```

### Section Types

1. **Hero** → Emoji, gradient headline, subtitle and maybe description
2. **Overview** → Gradient heading + simple highlight text
3. **Data Table** → Scrollable, hover rows, color-coded columns
4. **Benefits** → ✅ Grid of 4–6 key benefits in different sections or table or charts
5. **CTA** → Follow for more
**Note this is not hard and fast rule but you can use it

